data.meta_description: Dayton Review February 3, 1916  OBITUARY  Gustaf Adolf Gustafson was born in Torpa Parish, Östergötland, Sweden, September 14, 1846, and passed away at his home in Dayton January 25, 1916, aged 69 years, 4 months, 11 days. In 1853, he came to this country with his parents. Two of his sisters died of cholera on the ship...
